OL,4,G1900FUniversity Challenge
OL,5,     GThe University of Bristol plays
OL,6,     GDurham University in the first
OL,7,     Gmatch of the series, with a place
OL,8,     Gin the second round at stake.
OL,9,     GJeremy Paxman asks the questions.
OL,10,G1930FOnly Connect
OL,11,     GQuiz show presented by Victoria
OL,12,     GCoren in which patience and
OL,13,     Glateral thinking are as vital as
OL,14,     Gknowledge, and connections need
OL,15,     Gto be made between apparently
OL,16,     Gunconnected things.
OL,17,G2000FLost Cities of the Ancients
OL,18,     GDocumentary series which unearths
OL,19,     Glost civilisations and cities.
OL,20,     GThis edition visits northern Peru
OL,21,     Gto find the ruins of 250
OL,22,     Gmysterious pyramids.
